@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Frequently Asked Questions";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
            
            <div class="accordion mt-5" id="faqAccordion">
                <!-- Product Questions -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            What development services do you offer?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            We offer a range of web and software development services, including custom website development, e-commerce solutions, mobile app development, and API integrations. Our team specializes in a variety of programming languages and frameworks to ensure we can meet your specific project needs.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            How much does a typical project cost?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Project costs vary based on complexity, features required, and timeline. We provide detailed quotes after understanding your specific requirements. For small projects, pricing typically starts at $1,000, while more complex applications may range from $5,000-$50,000. Contact us for a personalized quote tailored to your project needs.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Ordering Questions -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            What is your typical development process?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Our development process typically includes:
                            <ol>
                                <li><strong>Discovery:</strong> Understanding your requirements and goals</li>
                                <li><strong>Planning:</strong> Creating project specifications and timeline</li>
                                <li><strong>Design:</strong> Developing wireframes and user interface mockups</li>
                                <li><strong>Development:</strong> Building the core functionality</li>
                                <li><strong>Testing:</strong> Quality assurance and bug fixing</li>
                                <li><strong>Deployment:</strong> Launching your application</li>
                                <li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Ongoing support and updates</li>
                            </ol>
                            We keep clients involved throughout the process with regular updates and feedback sessions.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            How long does a typical project take to complete?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Project timelines vary based on complexity and scope. Simple websites might take 2-4 weeks, while more complex web applications typically take 2-6 months. We provide detailed timelines during the planning phase and keep you updated on progress throughout development.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Support Questions -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                            Do you provide ongoing support after project completion?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Yes, we offer various support and maintenance packages to ensure your application continues to run smoothly after launch. These can include regular updates, security patches, performance optimization, and feature enhancements. We can tailor a support package to match your specific needs and budget.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            How do I request changes to my project after it's completed?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            For clients with active maintenance packages, you can submit change requests through our support portal or by contacting your dedicated project manager. For one-time changes, you can use the contact form on our website to describe your requirements, and we'll provide a quote for the requested modifications.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Technical Questions -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                            What technologies do you work with?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Our team is proficient in a wide range of technologies including:
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Angular, Vue.js</li>
                                <li><strong>Backend:</strong> ASP.NET Core, Node.js, Python, PHP, Java</li>
                                <li><strong>Mobile:</strong> React Native, Flutter, Swift, Kotlin</li>
                                <li><strong>Database:</strong> SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL, MongoDB</li>
                                <li><strong>Cloud Platforms:</strong> AWS, Azure, Google Cloud Platform</li>
                            </ul>
                            We're always learning and adapting to new technologies to ensure we can provide the best solutions for our clients.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingEight">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEight">
                            Can you help migrate an existing application or website?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseEight" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEight" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Yes, we specialize in helping businesses migrate their existing applications to newer technologies, different hosting environments, or improved architectures. Our migration services include thorough assessment, planning, execution, and testing to ensure a smooth transition with minimal downtime.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-5 text-center">
                <h3>Still have questions?</h3>
                <p>Feel free to contact us for any additional information or specific inquiries about our services.</p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary mt-2" open-sesame="createContactForm">Contact Us</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>